00:51:06.584 --> 00:51:08.836 line:90% position:50% align:center
and that would be fine.

00:51:08.836 --> 00:51:12.256 line:90% position:50% align:center
But by using jw.org,

00:51:12.256 --> 00:51:14.967 line:90% position:50% align:center
