00:51:14.967 --> 00:51:17.720 line:90% position:50% align:center
related articles,

00:51:17.720 --> 00:51:20.932 line:90% position:50% align:center
and videos right at her fingertips.

00:51:20.932 --> 00:51:23.559 line:90% position:50% align:center
The search page acted as her guide.

00:51:25.186 --> 00:51:29.106 line:90% position:50% align:center
