00:59:32.381 --> 00:59:34.842 line:90% position:50% align:center
This month’s postcard comes from Malaysia,

00:59:34.842 --> 00:59:39.054 line:90% position:50% align:center
a Southeast Asian country
renowned for its diversity.

00:59:41.348 --> 00:59:43.350 line:90% position:50% align:center
There are quiet farmlands,

00:59:43.350 --> 00:59:45.102 line:90% position:50% align:center
bustling cities,

00:59:45.102 --> 00:59:48.564 line:90% position:50% align:center
densely packed forests,
and calming coastlines.

00:59:49.356 --> 00:59:52.151 line:90% position:50% align:center
You’ll find a wide variety of creatures
like pygmy elephants,

00:59:53.235 --> 00:59:55.070 line:90% position:50% align:center
proboscis monkeys,

00:59:55.070 --> 00:59:57.281 line:90% position:50% align:center
and rhinoceros hornbills.

00:59:57.281 --> 01:00:00.409 line:90% position:50% align:center
Malaysia is home to wide ethnic diversity,

01:00:00.409 --> 01:00:02.911 line:90% position:50% align:center
displaying an amazing variety of clothing,

01:00:04.121 --> 01:00:06.373 line:90% position:50% align:center
languages, and delicious foods.

01:00:07.833 --> 01:00:10.210 line:90% position:50% align:center
Missionaries arrived
in the country in the 1930’s,

01:00:10.210 --> 01:00:12.337 line:90% position:50% align:center
and the truth began to spread.

01:00:12.337 --> 01:00:16.967 line:90% position:50% align:center
In the early 1950’s,
the first congregation was formed.

01:00:16.967 --> 01:00:20.471 line:90% position:50% align:center
Some of the missionaries
conducted 15 Bible studies a month.

01:00:21.430 --> 01:00:24.975 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our brothers and sisters
still find many righthearted people.

01:00:24.975 --> 01:00:27.519 line:90% position:50% align:center
The over 5,000 publishers

01:00:27.519 --> 01:00:30.564 line:90% position:50% align:center
average almost one Bible study per publisher!

01:00:31.648 --> 01:00:34.860 line:90% position:50% align:center
Many studies are conducted in longhouses,

01:00:34.860 --> 01:00:38.071 line:90% position:50% align:center
a collection of simple family homes
near the water,

01:00:38.071 --> 01:00:41.325 line:90% position:50% align:center
combined together and raised with stilts.

01:00:41.325 --> 01:00:43.327 line:90% position:50% align:center
Proverbs 9:3 says:

01:00:43.327 --> 01:00:47.998 line:90% position:50% align:center
“[Wisdom sends] out its female servants
to call out from the heights above.”

01:00:47.998 --> 01:00:52.085 line:90% position:50% align:center
You might say the sisters in Malaysia
take that verse literally,

01:00:52.085 --> 01:00:54.546 line:90% position:50% align:center
preaching high on Mount Kinabalu

01:00:54.546 --> 01:00:57.424 line:90% position:50% align:center
and across cable bridges
stretched over the forest.

01:00:58.425 --> 01:01:01.803 line:90% position:50% align:center
The 89 publishers
of the Keningau Congregation

01:01:01.803 --> 01:01:05.057 line:90% position:50% align:center
send their warm love
and greetings to you all.

01:01:07.184 --> 01:01:09.978 line:90% position:50% align:center
From the world headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

01:01:09.978 --> 01:01:12.648 line:90% position:50% align:center
this is JW Broadcasting.

